Henry Brandon (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Brandon_(actor) 0 Henry Brandon (June 8, 1912 – February 15, 1990) was a German-American film and stage character actor with a career spanning almost 60 years, involving more than one hundred films; he specialized in playing a wide diversity of ethnic roles.
